title: The Ultimate Marvel Max Torrent

The Ultimate Marvel Max Torrent

I am a huge fan of the Marvel Max comic books. So I thought it would be nice to share my collection. I have put a lot of work into this collection and I believe it is the biggest available. Extras and one shots are included! Okay...here goes the list of what this torrent contains, I hope you all enjoy!
